snippet.title: Stories One Pre-Alpha Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Pre-Alpha Launch Trailer for Stories One 
Download on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2494370/Stories_One/

⮟ Links and Info below ⮟
Website ‣ https://storiesone.com

⮟ Social Media ⮟

Twitter ‣ https://twitter.com/PlayStoriesOne
Facebook ‣ https://www.facebook.com/PlayStoriesOne
Reddit ‣ https://www.reddit.com/r/StoriesOne/

UNIQUE FUSION OF FPS AND MOBA
Welcome to Stories One: an exciting pre-alpha game blending FPS and MOBA genres. Embark on thrilling 5v5 battles in a 90's retro-futuristic city. Strategically build your deck, level up, and conquer your foes. Join the Stories One arena today!
